snippet.title: Sonic and The Fallen Star - CGS 2021
snippet.description:
Sonic and The Fallen Star is a 2D speed based platformer in the style of the 2D Classic Sonic games, with brand new visuals and colorful environments!
Will Eggman harness the true power of the stars, or will Sonic & Tails manage to fool his plans yet again?





Check the game as soon as the 18th hits!
https://chaogameshowcase.wixsite.com/cgs2021/games
